title: Manowar - The Lord Of Steel Remastered - Hammer Of God Edition (
description:
Today i serve you another remastered version of "The Lord Of Steel" - You get more Drums, more Guitar, less Bass, clearer Vocals. Give it a try, check it out, feel free to comment. Tracks are in ALAC, everything is high-quality. I tested the Tracks on several HiFi-systems, sound was alawys "clearer" and "fresher". Let me know if you like my releases and if I should continue my work! I also created as usual a different artwork. Enjoy!
